data.description: GULF VIEW UNIT with BRAND NEW LVP FLOORING JUST INSTALLED & BARN DOOR for a private sleeping bunk area! Here's your opportunity to own one of the best views in Laketown Wharf! Located on the 14th-floor, and the far southeast side of the building where you can enjoy amazing gulf views from the living room and balcony. Right off your front door, stunning unobstructed views of the heart of Panama City Beach over the Signal Hill Golf Course all the way to the south lagoon and St. Andrews State Park. The unit is located on the second stack and close to the elevators, so there is rarely foot traffic past your front door! Unit has 9ft Ceilings, 1,047 sqft., and comes fully furnished with all major appliances and stacked washer/dryer combo, turn-key, and rental ready to accommodate up to 6-guests. Enjoy resort-life with many shops on the ground level along with the 52,000 sqft. of lakefront Boardwalk and a nightly fountain & light show. Also, the house of Juan Taco, the best taqueria in PCB! Reasonable HOA fees include water, sewer, cable/TV, pest control plus amenities such as gated beach access, 5 community pools (1 heated year-round), kids Playground, hot tubs, mini-golf, Splash Bar & Grill, fitness center with gulf views, 2 covered parking garages and a dedicated gated beach access right next to Pineapple Willis. All information is deemed correct, buyers should verify if they are important.
